            <title><![CDATA[神舟十四号乘组进行第三次出舱活动]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-11/xxjpsgc007069_20221117_pepfn0a001.jpg?VersionId=M.MmRRepuKg4mjCgIl6MBqqUx7gHXhOs&amp;itok=w4bt5Xyi" title="神舟十四号乘组进行第三次出舱活动，这是中国空间站组装形成“T”字基本构型后的首次出舱活动。图为航天员陈冬成功出舱的画面。（新华社）" alt="神舟十四号乘组进行第三次出舱活动，这是中国空间站组装形成“T”字基本构型后的首次出舱活动。图为航天员陈冬成功出舱的画面。（新华社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-11/xxjpsgc007069_20221117_pepfn0a001.jpg?VersionId=M.MmRRepuKg4mjCgIl6MBqqUx7gHXhOs&amp;itok=w4bt5Xyi" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
