            <title><![CDATA[网传成都东风大桥现“毒狗”人士 警方：食物未检出有毒物质]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>成都网民反映“</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>毒狗人士”</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>在均隆街</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>滨河路东风大桥一带抛撒食物的视频在网络传播，引发关注。经调查，</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>成都锦江公安通报</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>食物未检出有毒物质。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>据澎湃新闻报道，</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>成都锦江公安</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>星期四（11月17日）</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>通报称，涉事人员姚某，女，51岁，黑龙江省齐齐哈尔市人，其于11月15日在成都某超市购买多包小米及面包，后到</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>成都锦江</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>区东风大桥周边绿化带附近作为鸟食进行抛撒。民警找到姚某时发现其随身物品中还剩有未投完的三包小米及四包面包。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>通报指，通过调阅事发地周边监控视频及对现场进行勘验检查，未发现其他可疑物质。经公安刑侦技术部门检验，现场遗留抛撒物和未投放的小米及面包均未检测出有毒物质，也未检测出网传的异烟肼成份。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
